extends LinuxLocalUserImpl
implements RedhatLinuxLocalUser

An implementation of the model object 'Redhat Linux Local User'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Account Disable After Days
  • Account Disable Date
  • Days Before Password May Change
  • Last Password Change
  • Password Expire After Days
  • Password Expire Warning Days
  • User Sid
